            <h3>Benefits of Home Loans</h3>
            <p>Home loans offer several advantages for those looking to buy a home:</p>
            <h5>Affordability:</h5>
            <p>Home loans allow you to spread the cost of a home over several years, making homeownership more accessible.</p>
            <h5>Tax Benefits: </h5>
            <p>Depending on your location, mortgage interest may be tax-deductible.</p>
            <h5>Equity Building: </h5>
            <p>Over time, your monthly mortgage payments help you build equity in your home.</p>
            <h5>Stability :</h5>
            <p>Fixed-rate mortgages offer predictable monthly payments, making budgeting easier.</p>
